{
  "stem": "10768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Still, so at the beginning, in order to help out the family-- father was orthodox.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He did not-- even though he was wearing gray clothes or-- but he wouldn't work on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mother was working as a, a, oh, what you call them in English?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two-- a watchmaker, a watchmaker, in an office building, so nothing would be taken away.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Mother also, also, Mother was at their time, taking in laundry from the Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The laundry was washed in a laundry establishment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Mother was ironing the shirts, before they went to the German-- not to the German, excuse me, to the Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So at the beginning, the first two or three weeks, I was helping mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was-- not Mother, I was ironing in order-- because we needed something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When we came there, bread was-- food was the biggest problem.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was established already that they were bringing flour to our town, and the bakery was baking bread.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they could not really-- since our town swell up with-- instead of 4,000 or 600, 6,000 people, we had, perhaps 15,000 or more from the all people who ran from the German territories to our, to our-- over.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they got stuck there, until they decided what to do with themselves, where to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So of course, the food supply was very, very critical.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Bread, sometimes you had to go at 4 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had to stay in line to get one kilo, which was two pounds of bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And by the time you came close to the door, they said it's all sold out, you have to wait for the next, for the next batch.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the food situation was very critical.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
